Package: EireR
Type: Package
Title: Harmonised Geospatial Data Access for the Island of Ireland
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Aoibhin", "Murphy",
      email = "aoibhinmurphy246@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides harmonised geospatial data for the island of Ireland,
    combining Republic of Ireland sources (EPA, Tailte Éireann) and Northern
    Ireland sources (DAERA, OpenDataNI). Auto-discovers 1023 datasets via
    EPA GeoServer WFS, ArcGIS Hub REST API, and OpenDataNI CKAN API.
    All data is returned in Irish Transverse Mercator (EPSG:2157).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
